==English==
===Etymology===
From ''un-'' + ''yoke''

===Transitive verb===
'''unyoke'''
#release something from a [[yoke]] or harness
#disconnect, unlink
#liberate, deliver from oppression

===Intransitive verb===
'''unyoke'''
#unyoke an animal
#cease from labour

